4:
The suffering of mankind is ever
present.
5:
I may have alighted upon a different
plane, but the cries of the weak still
call out to me. How unfortunate... I
shall make everything right.
7:
For I am their shepherd. You will be
lost sheep no more...
9:
Come, my servants. Bring salvation
unto this world.
16:
Fallen angel Olivia. I see you've
come after me.
19:
An unfamiliar place, an unknown
mana source... Could this be the
new world?
21:
Yes, that does appear to be the
case. Who'd have imagined we'd
end up here in the midst of our
battle.
22:
Regardless, I extend my salvation to
all, no matter where I am.
26:
The "salvation" you speak of only
breeds destruction. I won't let it
happen.
28:
Such power... I suppose I don't stand
a chance with my current vessel.
However...
34:
Though you may have been able to
traverse the portal, it's apparently
taken a toll on you.
36:
You're full of openings in your
weakened state. I'll be taking your
mana.
38:
You have my gratitude, fallen angel
Olivia. I am now able to extend the
hand of salvation to this world as
well.
45:
Struggle as you might, my salvation
is absolute.
80: Forgive me. I shall fight them off.
